---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="LoveAlwaysHere 首页" description="个人博客与工具集">
  <div class="container-page">
    <section class="pt-16 pb-12 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs tracking-widest mb-8 animate-fade-in" style="background-color:var(--accent-light);color:var(--bg-primary)">
        个人空间 · 技术博客 · 实用工具
      </div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.1s;animation-fill-mode:both">
        <span style="color:var(--accent)">探索</span>
        <span class="mx-3" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">·</span>
        <span style="color:var(--text-primary)">创造</span>
        <span class="mx-3" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">·</span>
        <span style="color:var(--accent)">分享</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">
        记录技术思考，分享实用工具。<br />
        在代码与创造之间，寻找属于自己的节奏。
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center animate-fade-up" style="animation-delay:0.3s;animation-fill-mode:both">
        <a href="/blog" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105" style="background-color:var(--accent);color:#fff">浏览随笔 →</a>
        <a href="/tools" class="px-8 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105" style="border:1px solid var(--border);color:var(--text-secondary)">实用工具</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <div class="card-warm animate-fade-up group" style="animation-delay:0.4s;animation-fill-mode:both">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-translate-y-1" style="background-color:var(--accent-light)">✍️</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold mb-3 transition-colors duration-300" style="color:var(--text-primary)">技术随笔</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">记录前端、全栈开发中的踩坑与思考，分享技术心得与最佳实践。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-warm animate-fade-up group" style="animation-delay:0.5s;animation-fill-mode:both">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-translate-y-1" style="background-color:var(--accent-light)">🔧</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold mb-3 transition-colors duration-300" style="color:var(--text-primary)">实用工具</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">日常开发和生活所需的在线小工具，开箱即用，持续更新。</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card-warm animate-fade-up group" style="animation-delay:0.6s;animation-fill-mode:both">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-xl mb-5 transition-all duration-500 group-hover:scale-110 group-hover:-translate-y-1" style="background-color:var(--accent-light)">🌱</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-serif font-semibold mb-3 transition-colors duration-300" style="color:var(--text-primary)">持续进化</h3>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">不断迭代优化，让这个小小的数字花园越来越丰富。</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-12 text-center">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-10">
        <div class="h-px flex-1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent)"></div>
        <span class="text-xs tracking-widest" style="color:var(--text-secondary)">最新动态</span>
        <div class="h-px flex-1" style="background:linear-gradient(to right, transparent, var(--border), transparent)"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="py-12">
        <div class="text-4xl mb-4" style="color:var(--accent)">✨</div>
        <p style="color:var(--text-secondary)">博客文章正在路上，敬请期待...</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</Layout>
